obj_root_law_sections_1_content:
  string
  line The
  line `Indian Easements Act, 1882 (V of 1882), is hereby extended to the territories respectively administered`
  line `by the Governor of Bombay in Council and the lieutenant-Governor of the ^1North-Western Provinces and`
  line `Chief Commissioner of Oudh.`
